;s:4:\"3081\";s:3:\"iid\";s:4:\"3906\";s:4:\"page\";s:1:\"1\";s:11:\"addon_title\";s:0:\"\";s:11:\"addon_frame\";s:74:\"<!--#p8_attach#-->/cms/item/2023_05/24_11/8dfef849f64178be.jpeg.cthumb.jpg\";s:13:\"addon_summary\";s:373:\"盐城市第一人民医院创建于1948年，经过七十余年的发展，现已建设成为一所集医疗、教学、科研、康复、急救为一体的三级甲等综合性医院。医院是首批国家级“住院医师规范化培训基地”、“全科医生临床培养建设基地”，承担南通大学、徐州医学院本科与研究生教学任务，及江\";s:2:\"ip\";s:10:\"172.16.1.2\";s:14:\"last_update_ip\";s:10:\"172.16.1.2\";s:9:\"timestamp\";s:10:\"1684897471\";s:7:\"content\";s:73026:\"<p style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">盐城市第一人民医院创建于<span>1948</span>年，经过七十余年的发展，现已建设成为一所集医疗、教学、科研、康复、急救为一体的三级甲等综合性医院。医院</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">是首批国家级“住院医师规范化培训基地”、“全科医生临床培养建设基地”，承担南通大学、徐州医学院本科与研究生教学任务，及江苏医药职业学院等十余所高校实习生带教工作<span>,</span>并于</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">2019</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">年正式挂牌南京大学医学院附属盐城第一人民医院。</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">医院共设有<span>4</span>个院区：主院区、北院区、五官科院区、儿童医院。</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">医院重视学科建设，建成了一批特色鲜明的重点专科，其中呼吸内科、骨科、普外科、心内科、检验科、影像科、肿瘤科、神经内科等<span>20</span>个科室被评为江苏省临床重点专科；市级临床重点专科<span>15</span>个；市医学重点学科<span>18</span>个。</span><br /></p><p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:32px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><img src=\"<!--#p8_attach#-->/cms/item/2023_05/24_11/8dfef849f64178be.jpeg.cthumb.jpg\" alt=\"医院1\" style=\"float: none;\" src=\"<!--#p8_attach#-->/cms/item/2023_05/24_11/8dfef849f64178be.jpeg.cthumb.jpg\" /></span></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:32px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">为了更好地选拔优秀人才，培养合格临床医师，我培训基地从即日起面向社会及各单位招收<span>2023</span>年度住院医师规范化培训社会化<span>/</span>单位委培养学员，现将有关事项公告如下：</span></p><p style=\"text-align:left;text-indent:32px;line-height:150%\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei; text-indent: 2em; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">一、基本条件：</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 28px; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span>1.<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-language-override: normal; font-feature-settings: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">坚持四项基本原则，</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">拥护党的路线、方针、政策，</span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">遵纪守法，品行端正，无违法违纪行为。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 28px; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span>2.<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-language-override: normal; font-feature-settings: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">高等院校西医医学类相应专业，普通本科以上学历的应、往届毕业生。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 28px; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span>3.<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-language-override: normal; font-feature-settings: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">身心健康，能胜任住院医师规范化培训的临床学习和工作。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 28px; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span>4.<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-language-override: normal; font-feature-settings: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">外语要求：原则上具备大学英语四级及以上合格证，报考紧缺专业外语要求可适当放宽。</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 28px; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei; text-indent: 2em; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\"><span>5.<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-language-override: normal; font-feature-settings: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">计算机水平达到国家或省计算机等级考试一级。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, Microsoft YaHei; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 150%;\">附加条件<span>1.</span>年龄要求：原则上本科生不超过<span>30</span>周岁，研究生不超过<span>35</span>周岁，紧缺专业年龄适当放宽。<span>2.</span>单位委培培训学员须出具在职证明及单位委培公函。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 28px; text-align: left; line-height: 2em; font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅